data.description: Pack your bags and move right in! This home has awesome updates including: new windows, new carpeting, whole home humidifier, new built-in entertainment center, and new insulated garage door! Furnace/AC, HWH and roof are all 8 years old. The open living room features vaulted ceilings and a wood burning fireplace. The roomy kitchen has plenty of space for an island and kitchen table.  Off the kitchen is a large 3 seasons room (with electric) that walks out to a deck and fenced back yard. The primary suite has its own bathroom and a large walk-in closet. Finishing the upstairs are two bedrooms and a full bath. The lower level has a large family room with new built-ins and a bathroom/laundry room. Washer and dryer are included in the sale! The two-car garage is oversized and has plenty of space for storage. Don’t miss the chance to own this gem. Schedule your showing today.  Move-in before Christmas!
